node.text: It’s been 3 years for my baby @theebutterflyproject. 3 years of tears and fears. Walking out on faith and believing God to take ya to higher ground. 3 years of supporting over 300+ women and mailing over 250+ women received survivor packs. 20 women clothed and countless inspired. God has been faithful through it all and for that I’m eternally grateful. We’re growing and only going up 🦋💜. Thank you to everyone who believes in me so they believe in The Butterfly Project. God, like Hannah, I give my baby back to you and will allow you to complete the good work you began! If you’d like to help celebrate our anniversary click the link to donate.
@r_marie.4 Ruthie!!! Thank you! I appreciate your kind words and support! 🥰
Kudos to you! You inspire me & everyone else. What a beautiful thing to also help all the survivors you have! To many more years of doing what you have been called to do! 💖
Hey we love your feed give us a dm!

Congratzzz Sis! Thankful for all you do ❤️
@theeashleyn thank you for watching over us and laying the smack down when needed! ❤️🦋💜
@yoshikobesq I believe you guys & love what you’re doing & stand for.
@martybmuzik thanks cuz! All glory to God!
@heartworktrending thanks sis! Thank you for going on this journey with me! ❤️

I’m so proud of you! Darling 💜💜💜
